%% Diagram: Service Worker streaming response relay using TransformStream
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor Page
    participant SW as Service Worker
    participant BE as Cache + Net
    participant TX as TransformStream

    Page->>SW: GET /article
    SW->>SW: respondWith(Response(readable))
    Note over SW,TX: Empty response is alive
    SW->>BE: cache.match(/shell.html)
    BE-->>SW: shell stream
    SW->>TX: shell.pipeTo(writable)
    SW->>BE: fetch(/api/article-body)
    BE-->>SW: body stream
    SW->>TX: body.pipeTo(writable)
    TX-->>Page: chunks streamed
    Note over Page: Shell first, body after
